      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LabAnalyzer是系统入口，它指向Active状态。还有一个小细节：在复合状态内部，DiagnosticEngine负责数字锁，HIPAA_Vault负责大小写锁，LabAnalyzer自己管滚动锁。这样划分是为了对应不同的安全模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "Active",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
