    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来构建这个结构。首先建立Active作为复合状态，内部用三个分隔区域（--）来组织三个并行状态机。第一区域放DiagnosticEngine和NumLockOff/NumLockOn的切换；第二区域放HIPAA_Vault和CapsLockOff/CapsLockOn；第三区域放LabAnalyzer和ScrollLockOff/ScrollLockOn。所有切换事件都按你说的命名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "NumLockOff",
        "NumLockOn",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
